---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import * as Header from './Header.md';
import profile from '../../assets/profile.png';
---

<div>
	<div class='pb-4 text-2xl font-bold'>
		<Header.Content />
	</div>

	<div>
		<div class='shadow-xl card lg:card-side bg-base-100'>
			<figure class='overflow-hidden'>
				<Image
					class='object-cover object-center w-full h-full'
					src={profile}
					alt='Profile'
				/>
			</figure>
			<div class='card-body'>
				<p>
					I am always looking for ideas for my next project. I love music, so I
					tend to lean towards music apps.
				</p>
				<div>
					<p>Here are some technologies I have been working with lately:</p>
					<ul class='list-disc list-inside'>
						<li>Go</li>
						<li>TypeScript, JavaScript</li>
						<li>React, Next.js</li>
						<li>React Native, Expo</li>
						<li>Express, Fastify</li>
						<li>PostgreSQL</li>
						<li>Python</li>
						<li>Java</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<p>
					Outside of programming, I am usually tinkering with <a
						class='link'
						href='https://reddit.com/r/customkeyboards'
						target='_blank'
						>keyboards</a
					>. I also enjoy <a
						href='/film'
						class='link'
						>film photography</a
					> and going on{' '}<a
						class='link'
						href='https://www.strava.com/athletes/60272710'
						target='blank'
						>runs</a
					> to clear my mind.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
